            <title><![CDATA[【还在低头玩手机吗？#低头60度相当于颈椎负重40斤#[吃惊]】#长期低头对颈椎伤害有多大#低头时，颈椎受力会增加3-5倍，低头超过60°，如同一个40斤的小朋友坐在...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【还在低头玩手机吗？<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BD%8E%E5%A4%B460%E5%BA%A6%E7%9B%B8%E5%BD%93%E4%BA%8E%E9%A2%88%E6%A4%8E%E8%B4%9F%E9%87%8D40%E6%96%A4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BD%8E%E5%A4%B460%E5%BA%A6%E7%9B%B8%E5%BD%93%E4%BA%8E%E9%A2%88%E6%A4%8E%E8%B4%9F%E9%87%8D40%E6%96%A4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#低头60度相当于颈椎负重40斤#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E4%BD%8E%E5%A4%B4%E5%AF%B9%E9%A2%88%E6%A4%8E%E4%BC%A4%E5%AE%B3%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E5%A4%A7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%95%BF%E6%9C%9F%E4%BD%8E%E5%A4%B4%E5%AF%B9%E9%A2%88%E6%A4%8E%E4%BC%A4%E5%AE%B3%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E5%A4%A7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#长期低头对颈椎伤害有多大#</span></a>低头时，颈椎受力会增加3-5倍，低头超过60°，如同一个40斤的小朋友坐在脖子上。长期低头会造成颈椎后方肌肉劳损，颈椎曲度变直。医生建议，将电脑、书籍放在平视的位置，睡觉时选择高度适宜的枕头，有助于缓解颈椎不适。 <a href="http://t.cn/A6Ch0KIl" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
