            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E6%9D%AF%E5%8F%AF%E4%B9%90%E7%BD%90%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E7%83%9F%E5%9D%87%E4%B8%BA%E4%BC%AA%E5%8A%A3%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E6%9D%AF%E5%8F%AF%E4%B9%90%E7%BD%90%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E7%83%9F%E5%9D%87%E4%B8%BA%E4%BC%AA%E5%8A%A3%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#奶茶杯可乐罐电子烟均为伪劣产品#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%B6%8570%E4%B8%87%E6%94%AF%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E7%83%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%9F%A5%E8%8E%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%B6%8570%E4%B8%87%E6%94%AF%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E7%83%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%9F%A5%E8%8E%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#超70万支非法电子烟被查获#</span></a>国家烟草专卖局近期开展奶茶杯、可乐罐等非法调味电子烟整治工作，查获72.38万支，涉案金额5.07亿元。据悉，奶茶杯、可乐罐调味电子烟均为非法生产的伪劣电子烟产品，对心智未成熟的未成年人有较强诱导性；且添加成分复杂，安全隐患突出。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%8E%A7%E7%83%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳控烟#</span></a>  <a href="http://t.cn/A6CPJ3FA" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
